body_text.text: Nucleotide Sequences 1986 Sequences /1987 Volume VI Citation Index
The Citation Index lists the citations for all of the articles cited in the sequence entries in Volume VI of this compendium.

The abbreviations that are used for journal names in the Citation Index as well as the number of citations listed for each journal are tabulated at the beginning of the index. The names of all entries citing a particular article follow the citation for that article. Use the GenBank Entry Index to determine the page on which each entry begins. A complete Master Citation Index to all eight volumes is included in Volume VIII.
